title: Is This Sustainable?
description:
Emily Kaplan and Linda Cohn dive right into the latest from around the league as a crazy week of hockey unfolds. After that, Edmonton Oilers defensemen Darnell Nurse joins the show to talk about his latest project and how the Oilers are doing so far this season.
